comments: Had class on Sat am\'s and Sean was very understanding of people being awake so early. He was helpful and would spend extra time available for questions after class; related the class to real life experiences and got students involved in conversations so it was more memorable.
Very good teacher!! Explains everything very well and willing to help the students. Would def take another class with him!!

Clear and concise. He is very helpful and takes a subject which is sometimes difficult and makes it easier to understand. Fair in his grading and conducts class as you would expect a high caliber professor to.
